@node "Intro" "Introduction"

 @{b}@{fg highlight}Introduction
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}@{fg text}
   I decided to write this tiny tool, when I uploaded
   some tools to aminet for the first time. I missed
   a utility with it it would be easy to realize the
   creation of a .readme file for an archive.
   So ARC was born.
@endnode

@node "Require" "Requirements"

 @{b}@{fg highlight}Requirements
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~@{ub}@{fg text}
    OS 2.04+
    some RAM ;)
    Ed  (workbench included)
    Lha   (Aminet: Lha194.lha) located in C:

    If you want to use the update feature for the Aminetź Index List,
    then you'll also need
    
    wget  (Aminet: wget-bin.lha) located in C:

  @{i}Developers also need@{ui}

    SimpleCat 1.2 (or any program that is similar to it
                   and does the same job)
@endnode

